(412, 1, '2016-12-16 08:26:16', '2016-12-16 08:26:16', '<ul class=\"a-vertical a-spacing-none\">\r\n <li><span class=\"a-list-item\">FEATURING 21 TOOLS: Needlenose pliers, regular pliers, 154CM replaceable wire cutters, 154CM replaceable hard-wire cutters, stranded-wire cutters, electrical crimper, wire stripper, 420HC knife, saw, spring-action scissors, awl w/thread loop, ruler (8in, 19cm), can opener, bottle opener, wood/metal file, diamond coated file, blade exchanger, large bit driver, large screwdriver, small screwdriver.</span></li>\r\n <li><span class=\"a-list-item\">ALL LOCKING FEATURES: All locking features mean that every tool and knife on the body of the handle, with the exception of the plier head, will lock into place. The all locking design enables you to operate individual tools safely and effectively. By locking them into place when fully open, you can put pressure on the implement while safely completing the job, before manually unlocking the tool to stow it away.</span></li>\r\n <li><span class=\"a-list-item\">OUTSIDE-ACCESSIBLE TOOLS: The Surge features tools that are accessible while the tool is in its folded or closed position, mimicking the functionality of a pocket knife. In addition, the Surge includes a secure ring for attaching the tool safely and securely to a lanyard. Often people who work near water or on scaffolding attach their tool to a lanyard on their person to avoid losing the tool if it\'s dropped.</span></li>\r\n <li><span class=\"a-list-item\">ONE-HANDED OPERABLE: Every feature on the Surge can be opened and operated with one hand. This enables you to keep the other hand free for situations that require multi-tasking or a free hand.</span></li>\r\n <li><span class=\"a-list-item\">ONE TOOL. A COUPLE THOUSAND USES.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Leatherman - Surge Multi-Tool', '<ul class=\"a-vertical a-spacing-none\">\r\n <li><span class=\"a-list-item\">FEATURING 21 TOOLS: Needlenose pliers, regular pliers, 154CM replaceable wire cutters